# 🧪 MAGELLAN-FORGE — Backend Test Scenarios

**Status:** ⏳ Awaiting Approval  
**Engine:** `MAGELLAN-FORGE-V1` | `http://localhost:8080/api`  
**Scope:** All 7 REST endpoints across the [UnifiedParserController](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/controller/UnifiedParserController.java#22-371)

---

## 📋 Endpoints Under Test

| #   | Method | Endpoint                   | Purpose                                        |
| --- | ------ | -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| 1   | GET    | `/api/health`              | Health check                                   |
| 2   | GET    | `/api/layouts`             | Fetch layout definitions                       |
| 3   | POST   | `/api/parse`               | Parse file (multipart upload)                  |
| 4   | POST   | `/api/parse-text`          | Parse raw text (body)                          |
| 5   | POST   | `/api/convert/mrx-to-ack`  | Convert MRX → ACK                              |
| 6   | POST   | `/api/convert/mrx-to-resp` | Convert MRX → RESP                             |
| 7   | POST   | `/api/convert/mrx-to-csv`  | Convert MRX → CSV                              |
| 8   | POST   | `/api/validate`            | Validate claim (STATUS_CHANGE / PARTIAL_UNITS) |

---

## 🗂️ Category 1: Smoke Tests

> Quick sanity — API is alive and serving.

### SC-01 · Health Check

- **Endpoint:** `GET /api/health`
- **Input:** None
- **Expected:** `200 OK` · `{ "status": "UP", "engine": "MAGELLAN-FORGE-V1" }`
- **Tags:** `smoke`

### SC-02 · Layouts Available

- **Endpoint:** `GET /api/layouts`
- **Input:** None
- **Expected:** `200 OK` · Response body contains keys: `MRX`, `ACK`, `RESP`
- **Tags:** `smoke`

---

## 🗂️ Category 2: Functional (Happy Path) Tests

> Core business flows with valid inputs.

### FP-01 · Parse MRX File (Multipart)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · field `file` = valid MRX `.txt` file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "MRX"`
  - `summary.total > 0`
  - `summary.invalid == 0`
  - `lines[0].type == "Header"`
  - `lines[last].type == "Trailer"`
  - `validationErrors` is `null` or empty
- **Tags:** `functional`, [parse](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/controller/UnifiedParserController.java#116-146), `mrx`

### FP-02 · Parse ACK File (Multipart)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · field `file` = valid ACK `.txt` file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "ACK"`
  - `summary.total > 0`
  - Has Header, Data, and Trailer lines
- **Tags:** `functional`, [parse](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/controller/UnifiedParserController.java#116-146), `ack`

### FP-03 · Parse RESP File (Multipart)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · field `file` = valid RESP `.txt` file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "RESP"`
  - `summary.total > 0`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [parse](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/controller/UnifiedParserController.java#116-146), `resp`

### FP-04 · Parse MRX Text (Raw Body)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse-text`
- **Input:** `text/plain` body = content of valid MRX file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "MRX"`
  - Same shape as FP-01
- **Tags:** `functional`, `parse-text`, `mrx`

### FP-05 · Parse ACK Text (Raw Body)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse-text`
- **Input:** `text/plain` body = content of valid ACK file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "ACK"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, `parse-text`, `ack`

### FP-06 · Parse RESP Text (Raw Body)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/parse-text`
- **Input:** `text/plain` body = content of valid RESP file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `detectedSchema: "RESP"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, `parse-text`, `resp`

### FP-07 · Convert MRX → ACK (All Accepted)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file · no params
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `{ "content": "...", "fileName": "TEST.MCMSMN_CLAIMS_ACK_*.txt" }`
  - Generated ACK has 1 Header + N Data + 1 Trailer lines
  - All Data lines have `Status = "A"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `mrx-to-ack`

### FP-08 · Convert MRX → ACK (With Reject Percentage)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file · `rejectPercentage=30`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - ~30% of Data lines have `Status = "R"` with `Reject ID` and `Reject Reason`
  - Remaining lines have `Status = "A"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `reject-percentage`

### FP-09 · Convert MRX → ACK (With Reject Count)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file · `rejectCount=5`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - Exactly 5 Data lines have `Status = "R"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `reject-count`

### FP-10 · Convert MRX → ACK (Randomize Reject Codes)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file · `rejectPercentage=50` · `randomizeRejectCodes=true`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - Rejected lines have varied `Reject ID` values (not all `EDI3108`)
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `reject-codes`

### FP-11 · Convert MRX → ACK (Custom Timestamp)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX · `timestamp=20260209202425`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `fileName` contains `20260209202425`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `timestamp`

### FP-12 · Convert MRX → RESP (All Approved / PD)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-resp`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file · no params
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - All Data lines have `MRx Claim Status = "PD"`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `mrx-to-resp`

### FP-13 · Convert MRX → RESP (With Deny Percentage)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-resp`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX · `denyPercentage=40`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - ~40% of eligible (units > 1) lines have `MRx Claim Status = "DY"`
  - Claims with `Units/Quantity = 1` must NOT be denied
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `deny-percentage`

### FP-14 · Convert MRX → RESP (With Partial Percentage)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-resp`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX · `partialPercentage=30`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - ~30% of eligible lines have `MRx Claim Status = "PA"`
  - PA lines: `Units approved > 0` AND `Units Denied > 0` AND `Units approved > Units Denied`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `partial-percentage`

### FP-15 · Convert MRX → RESP (Combined Deny + Partial)

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-resp`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · `denyPercentage=20` · `partialPercentage=30`
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - Deny set and partial set are **mutually exclusive** (no claim in both)
  - Remaining claims are `PD`
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `combined-scenario`

### FP-16 · Convert MRX → CSV

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-csv`
- **Input:** `multipart/form-data` · valid MRX file
- **Expected:**
  - `200 OK`
  - `{ "content": "...", "fileName": "TEST.MCMSMN_CLAIMS_EXPORT_*.csv" }`
  - Content starts with a CSV header row
  - Row count equals MRX data line count
- **Tags:** `functional`, [convert](file:///d:/Antigravity/AntiGravity_Kit/magellen-responce/backend/src/main/java/com/mrx/fileparserengine/service/UnifiedParserService.java#861-873), `mrx-to-csv`

