## 🗂️ Category 7: ACK Line Structure Correctness

> Verify generated ACK file has correct structure per spec.

### ACK-01 · ACK Line Length

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** Valid MRX
- **Expected:** Every line in the generated ACK content has length == ACK spec line length (220)
- **Tags:** `functional`, `ack-structure`

### ACK-02 · ACK Header Fields

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** Valid MRX with timestamp `20260209202425`
- **Expected:** Header line (starts with `H`) contains:
  - `"PRIME"` in Sender field
  - `"BCBSMN"` in Receiver field
  - Date `"20260209"` in Date field
  - Original file reference in File Name field
- **Tags:** `functional`, `ack-structure`, `header`

### ACK-03 · ACK Trailer Record Count

- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/convert/mrx-to-ack`
- **Input:** Valid MRX with N data lines
- **Expected:** Trailer `Total Records` field == N (exact match)
- **Tags:** `functional`, `ack-structure`, `trailer`

